title: 103: First Round Draft Buzz
itunes:title: 103: First Round Draft Buzz
description:
Daniel Jeremiah joins Bucky Brooks from a very windy Chicago before the 2016 NFL Draft to break down the top ten from their mocks and the latest buzz surrounding the draft. The guys also give you the players to watch from the second and third days of the draft.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
